# See https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file.
#
# Applied to the proxy image build, whose context is cmd/proxy (not the
# repo root, so the root .dockerignore does not apply).
#
# Excludes proxy_test.go so test edits do not invalidate the build layer
# and force a Go rebuild.

**

!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

!go.mod
!go.sum
